style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">FloatingToc</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div></figure>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"controlled\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#controlled\" class=\"peer\">Controlled</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "floating-toc-controlled"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"custom-delays\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#custom-delays\" class=\"peer\">Custom Delays</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "floating-toc-custom-delays"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"hierarchical\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#hierarchical\" class=\"peer\">Hierarchical